item.title: Machine Learning in Nmap
item.description: Notes The original post has been published on the Amossys blog I present some pieces of codes which are originally commented by their authors. I keep authors’ comments under the format /* comments */ while my own comments use the format // comments. I use the version 7.70SVN of nmap. First discovery After installing a basic Raspbian on my RPi, I also decided to add nmap to the system.
